@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### PEOPLE-GROWTH MODULE - Employee Development
### ============================================

### GAPS - List Learning Gaps
GET {{baseUrl}}/people-growth/gaps?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: {{token}}

### GAPS - Get Gap Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/people-growth/gaps/:gapId
Authorization: {{token}}

### GAPS - Close Gap
POST {{baseUrl}}/people-growth/gaps/:gapId/close
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completionDate": "2025-01-10"
}

### GAPS - Get Learning Paths for Gap
GET {{baseUrl}}/people-growth/gaps/:gapId/learning-paths
Authorization: {{token}}

### TEAM - Get Team Report
GET {{baseUrl}}/people-growth/team/report
Authorization: {{token}}

### TEAM - Get Team Heatmap
GET {{baseUrl}}/people-growth/team/heatmap
Authorization: {{token}}

### PROFILE - Get My Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/people-growth/my-profile
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
